about how cold it is?

16:33.840 --> 16:35.960
I was sweaty and I catch colds easily.

16:36.040 --> 16:37.480
My throat is delicate--

16:37.560 --> 16:40.480
Calcare, my job is to be your conscience.

16:40.560 --> 16:43.800
I must verify whether you know
why you keep going on about the cold.

16:43.880 --> 16:46.120
